  <section>
    <p>Invisalign is a modern solution for straightening teeth without the inconvenience of metal braces. At <strong>Potomac Crown Dentistry</strong> in <strong>North Potomac, MD</strong>, we help patients achieve beautiful, aligned smiles using custom-made clear aligners that are comfortable, removable, and nearly invisible.</p>

    <h2>Why Choose Invisalign?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Discreet clear aligners that blend with your smile</li>
      <li>Removable for meals, brushing, and flossing</li>
      <li>No food restrictions</li>
      <li>Fewer visits compared to traditional braces</li>
      <li>Backed by advanced 3D treatment planning</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Trusted Invisalign Provider in North Potomac</h2>
    <p><a href="https://potomaccrowndentistry.com/services/invisalign/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Potomac Crown Dentistry</a> is a Top 1% Diamond Invisalign Provider in North America. Led by Dr. Richard Cantwell, our clinic offers advanced Invisalign treatment with precise digital scanning and a personalized care approach trusted by the local community.</p>

    <h2>What to Expect</h2>
    <p>Your Invisalign journey starts with a consultation and digital iTero scan. From there, we design a custom treatment plan and provide your first set of aligners. You’ll change aligners every 1–2 weeks and return for periodic check-ins to track progress.</p>

    <h2>Cost and Insurance</h2>
    <p>Invisalign costs generally range from $3,000 to $6,500. Many dental insurance plans offer partial coverage. Our team can help verify your benefits and offer financing options to make your smile makeover affordable.</p>

